The '''Figg & Associates Art Museum''' was a museum in [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]]. For a brief time, a [[Carbonite/Legends|carbonite]] block containing the frozen body of [[Trioculus]] was displayed there under the orders of [[Zorba Desilijic Tiure]].

